main event: A civilian observed two red objects in the sky for one and a half hours in Orlando, Florida on March 25, 1961.
interesting points: Both objects appeared round and red and were situated some distance apart,One of the objects was approximately 50 degrees azimuth and the other at 45 degrees azimuth,The smaller object flashed white once or twice,The objects were visible when the observer went indoors,The local planetarium reported that the planets Mars and Jupiter were in the area at the time of the sighting.
sighted object: two red objects in the sky
witness description: Civilian, Mrs. B, 44 years old, 2 years college education
